n=int(input('Enter n value:'))
esum=0
osum=0
for i in range(1,n+1):
    if(i%2==0):
        esum=esum+i
    else:
        osum=osum+i
print('The sum of even numbers is',esum)
print('The sum of odd numbers is',osum)

Output
Enter n value:

20 

The sum of even numbers is 110
The sum of odd numbers is 100 


